OL,10,     Fdiscoveries before the payments
OL,11,     Fare made and the winner is
OL,12,     Fannounced.
OL,13,G1750 George Clarke's Old House New Home
OL,14,     FIn Yorkshire, George takes on a
OL,15,     Fproject that is part period house,
OL,16,     Fpart dog's dinner. In
OL,17,     FBuckinghamshire, the thought of a
OL,18,     Fcorner cocktail bar proves a real
OL,19,     Ftonic.
